source.name: U.S. Treasury-Owned Gold
source.description: Reflects gold bullion and gold coins owned by the federal government. Summarizes the fine troy ounces and the book value of gold held by various facilities. Identifies the value of gold coins and bullion on display at Federal Reserve banks; coins and bullion in reserve at the Federal Reserve Bank of New York; and gold held by U.S. Mint facilities
